title: Did A "Feeling" Save The Lives Of Two Teens? | True Ghost Stories
description:
Today on another chilling episode of Real Ghost Stories Online. 

When two young people have the urge for a late night snack, the idea of having a paranormal encounter was the furthest thing from their minds. 

Especially when one of them has a sudden urge to leave the road they are traveling down. 

It would turn out to be a turn that saved their lives. 

We hear that story and much more, today, on Real Ghost Stories Online.
